and then comes back
to the center.

1370
01:08:19,115 --> 01:08:21,150
And that's where he goes down.

1371
01:08:21,285 --> 01:08:22,319
Right.

1372
01:08:22,453 --> 01:08:26,055
My guess is,
he can't get out of this bay

1373
