1557
01:19:47,837 --> 01:19:53,443
And you say this fish
took down a boat?

1558
01:19:54,412 --> 01:19:55,645
Yes, Sir.

1559
01:19:56,613 --> 01:19:58,515
[dramatic music]

1560
01:19:59,317 --> 01:20:00,951
We're gonna need a bigger one.

